{"tw": {"3028830": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "外族娘！請好好保護我吧！", "steam_appid": 3028830, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人類太過弱小了！想要縱橫天下，唯有倚靠*外族娘*！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1bda705694778de6ebc64d1975dfc0ce.avif?t=1776310131\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras_big/1bda705694778de6ebc64d1975dfc0ce.webp?t=1776310131 width=1560 height=918 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【遊戲系統】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有別一般Roguelite RPG遊戲，本作採用小隊作戰系統。 一眾外族娘夥伴們各有其作戰特色，在戰鬥中玩家能按照狀況及戰術，選擇不同的陣容組合。獨特的戰鬥輪盤設計，令這款遊戲在倖存者like的中脫穎而出，不再只是單純的走位而加入了更多技巧上的操控！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲提供共19個獨特關卡，你必須突破重重危機，擊倒一眾實力強橫的BOSS，且要一邊與時間競賽，搶在時限內完成跑圖。善用戰鬥輪盤的“旋回”功能，隨時切換外族娘的陣型排列，以發揮她們的最大效能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不論你只希望追求OP的快感，還是你只想守護你的推角，都可以在《外族娘！》中找到樂趣。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【劇情】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自幼失去父親的廢宅青年「阿祖」，一天被交予了父親的神奇遺物後，決心出門冒險，找出父親消失的原因。  <br>一無是處的阿祖在路上認識到各色各樣，各自有其故事的外族娘。憑著外族娘們的強大實力，與遺物的神秘力量，阿祖一步一步接近父親消失的真相。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【特色】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    充滿戰術性的小隊戰系統為每場戰鬥增添變化。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各種強力升級在戰鬥中等你發現。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王道RPG敘事模式，戰鬥內外皆有劇情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19個獨立設計的故事關卡，7個原創劇情大BOSS等你征服！拒絕作業式循環！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6名各有魅力，擁有獨立劇情的外族娘與你出生入死。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18組全手繪H場景，12組live2D動態配上電影感鏡頭。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【外族娘介紹】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/3da54d091a264f84325e2877a3a6f5f7.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/3da54d091a264f84325e2877a3a6f5f7.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/3da54d091a264f84325e2877a3a6f5f7.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>修蘿</strong> <br>來自北方蠻族的高原戰士。實力強大外加性格火爆，是名可靠又可怕的忠實夥伴。她能在戰鬥中以強壯的身軀為隊友抵擋敵人，打飛一切礙事的傢伙。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/7396657bb544e8ec56a0536aa083bcff.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/7396657bb544e8ec56a0536aa083bcff.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/7396657bb544e8ec56a0536aa083bcff.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>阿莉絲</strong> <br>從地底來的精銳獵手。貌似天真無邪卻隱藏著不為人知的一面，難以觸摸。矯捷的她能使用弓弩狙擊遠方敵人，並能用狼及陷阱進行各種牽制。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/d850144f623f6bfca09d9fb87d026668.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/d850144f623f6bfca09d9fb87d026668.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/d850144f623f6bfca09d9fb87d026668.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潔莎蓮</strong> <br>魅惑的惡魔法師。有著跟其邪惡外表完全不同的溫柔性格，是位喜愛「照顧」人的色氣大姊姊。她的烈焰魔法能一下子蒸發眼前的敵群，破壞力超卓。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/98a4fd14cf76c746a778d51b348a7100.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/98a4fd14cf76c746a778d51b348a7100.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/98a4fd14cf76c746a778d51b348a7100.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小蘭</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >江湖人稱黑蘭花的女飛賊。英姿颯爽且為人處事認真，並有著一段不堪回首的過去。身手不凡的她不但擅長投擲各種暗器，還是個用毒高手。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b0712137ced37875521c7bc48b0e84cf.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b0712137ced37875521c7bc48b0e84cf.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b0712137ced37875521c7bc48b0e84cf.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>珊妮</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >獨居於沼澤的哥布林薩滿。擁有哥布林千百代祖先智慧的她性格卻是惡劣無比。會使用巫術詛咒四周大地，讓大範圍的敵人持續受到傷害。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1b49b5f4f8a56876aaae9c1695bf746e.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1b49b5f4f8a56876aaae9c1695bf746e.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1b49b5f4f8a56876aaae9c1695bf746e.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>霧月</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孤高的蜥蜴人俠客，忠肝義膽。家族慘遭屠殺的她正在拼死追趕著一名危險無比的殺人鬼。她的劍術能瞬間給予敵人巨大的傷害，非常致命。</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人類太過弱小了！想要縱橫天下，唯有倚靠*外族娘*！<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1bda705694778de6ebc64d1975dfc0ce.avif?t=1776310131\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras_big/1bda705694778de6ebc64d1975dfc0ce.webp?t=1776310131 width=1560 height=918 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【遊戲系統】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有別一般Roguelite RPG遊戲，本作採用小隊作戰系統。 一眾外族娘夥伴們各有其作戰特色，在戰鬥中玩家能按照狀況及戰術，選擇不同的陣容組合。獨特的戰鬥輪盤設計，令這款遊戲在倖存者like的中脫穎而出，不再只是單純的走位而加入了更多技巧上的操控！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲提供共19個獨特關卡，你必須突破重重危機，擊倒一眾實力強橫的BOSS，且要一邊與時間競賽，搶在時限內完成跑圖。善用戰鬥輪盤的“旋回”功能，隨時切換外族娘的陣型排列，以發揮她們的最大效能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不論你只希望追求OP的快感，還是你只想守護你的推角，都可以在《外族娘！》中找到樂趣。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【劇情】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自幼失去父親的廢宅青年「阿祖」，一天被交予了父親的神奇遺物後，決心出門冒險，找出父親消失的原因。  <br>一無是處的阿祖在路上認識到各色各樣，各自有其故事的外族娘。憑著外族娘們的強大實力，與遺物的神秘力量，阿祖一步一步接近父親消失的真相。  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【特色】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    充滿戰術性的小隊戰系統為每場戰鬥增添變化。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各種強力升級在戰鬥中等你發現。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >王道RPG敘事模式，戰鬥內外皆有劇情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19個獨立設計的故事關卡，7個原創劇情大BOSS等你征服！拒絕作業式循環！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6名各有魅力，擁有獨立劇情的外族娘與你出生入死。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18組全手繪H場景，12組live2D動態配上電影感鏡頭。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【外族娘介紹】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/3da54d091a264f84325e2877a3a6f5f7.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/3da54d091a264f84325e2877a3a6f5f7.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/3da54d091a264f84325e2877a3a6f5f7.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>修蘿</strong> <br>來自北方蠻族的高原戰士。實力強大外加性格火爆，是名可靠又可怕的忠實夥伴。她能在戰鬥中以強壯的身軀為隊友抵擋敵人，打飛一切礙事的傢伙。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/7396657bb544e8ec56a0536aa083bcff.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/7396657bb544e8ec56a0536aa083bcff.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/7396657bb544e8ec56a0536aa083bcff.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>阿莉絲</strong> <br>從地底來的精銳獵手。貌似天真無邪卻隱藏著不為人知的一面，難以觸摸。矯捷的她能使用弓弩狙擊遠方敵人，並能用狼及陷阱進行各種牽制。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/d850144f623f6bfca09d9fb87d026668.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/d850144f623f6bfca09d9fb87d026668.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/d850144f623f6bfca09d9fb87d026668.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潔莎蓮</strong> <br>魅惑的惡魔法師。有著跟其邪惡外表完全不同的溫柔性格，是位喜愛「照顧」人的色氣大姊姊。她的烈焰魔法能一下子蒸發眼前的敵群，破壞力超卓。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/98a4fd14cf76c746a778d51b348a7100.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/98a4fd14cf76c746a778d51b348a7100.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/98a4fd14cf76c746a778d51b348a7100.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小蘭</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >江湖人稱黑蘭花的女飛賊。英姿颯爽且為人處事認真，並有著一段不堪回首的過去。身手不凡的她不但擅長投擲各種暗器，還是個用毒高手。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b0712137ced37875521c7bc48b0e84cf.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b0712137ced37875521c7bc48b0e84cf.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b0712137ced37875521c7bc48b0e84cf.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>珊妮</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >獨居於沼澤的哥布林薩滿。擁有哥布林千百代祖先智慧的她性格卻是惡劣無比。會使用巫術詛咒四周大地，讓大範圍的敵人持續受到傷害。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1b49b5f4f8a56876aaae9c1695bf746e.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1b49b5f4f8a56876aaae9c1695bf746e.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1b49b5f4f8a56876aaae9c1695bf746e.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>霧月</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >孤高的蜥蜴人俠客，忠肝義膽。家族慘遭屠殺的她正在拼死追趕著一名危險無比的殺人鬼。她的劍術能瞬間給予敵人巨大的傷害，非常致命。</p></li></ul>", "short_description": "新感覺小隊戰Roguelite動作RPG！帶著一眾實力高強，且充滿個性的外族娘闖蕩江湖，組合出屬於你的最強陣容！從戰鬥中推進劇情發展，讓外族娘們向你躺開心扉，俘虜她們的身與心。", "supported_languages": "繁體中文, 英文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/1229d7badaba6db4014e1d0166a8618bbf13b2a0/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1776310131", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/05309bd003d61b48b9ac3002ae7846d238af5ce6/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1776310131", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/05309bd003d61b48b9ac3002ae7846d238af5ce6/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1776310131", "website": null, "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 560 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 5.24 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows7/8/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i3<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 8 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 760 / AMD Radeon HD 6870  DirectX 版本: 11<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 5.3 GB 可用空間<br></li><li><strong>音效卡:</strong> DirectSound</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "developers": ["Volcanic Good Boy"], "publishers": ["LewdLoco"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 26000, "final": 23400, "discount_percent": 10, "initial_formatted": "NT$ 260", "final_formatted": "NT$ 234"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 28, "description": "完全支援控制器"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "1", "description": "動作"}, {"id": "4", "description": "休閒"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}, {"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2026 年 4 月 15 日"}}}}, "us": {"3028830": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Stranger Maidens Please Protect Me!", "steam_appid": 3028830, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humans are weak! You can’t go anywhere without your STRANGER MAIDENS!<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1bda705694778de6ebc64d1975dfc0ce.avif?t=1776310131\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras_big/1bda705694778de6ebc64d1975dfc0ce.webp?t=1776310131 width=1560 height=918 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Game System】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not like your typical Roguelike Survivor, this game focuses on an innovative Squad Based Combat System. Adept to various challenges with a diverse cast of Stranger Maidens, build your ultimate team to eliminate your foes.<br><br>   Explore 19 handcrafted stages, conquer perilous hazards and stage gimmicks, defeat challenging bosses all the while racing against the clock. Utilize the unique &quot;TEAM ROTATION&quot; mechanic to unleash the full potential of the ladies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you want optimize your way to victory, or you just want to hangout with your favorite girls, “Stranger Maidens” will provide you with a satisfying experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Story】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Joey, a loser who was traumatised by the loss of his father. One day you received a mysterious artefact left by your father, and you are determined to go on an adventure to find out what happened to him. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In your journey you will encounter a variety of beautiful yet mysterious Strangers Maidens, each with their own story to tell. Combining their combat prowess and the strange power of the artefact, you come closer to the truth with every step…</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Feature】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Tactical Squad Based Combat System provides many possibilities in every battle.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Powerful upgrades await your discovery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional RPG narration style, you get stories both in and out of combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19 uniquely designed story stages, 7 fearsome story bosses with unique design and challenge, no more repetitive gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Stranger Maidens each with their own story and unique charm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 fully hand drawn sex scenes, 12 live2D animated with dynamic cameras.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Stranger Maidens】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/03ee57c239d2cda15988198c2651fb3a.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/03ee57c239d2cda15988198c2651fb3a.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/03ee57c239d2cda15988198c2651fb3a.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shu’Rah</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Barbarian warrior of the Northern Highland. With combat ferocity as explosive as her temperament, she is a reliable companion who is to be admired and feared. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Combat, Shu’Rah uses her exceptional physique to stand between the enemies and her team, keeping all dangers away from her teammates. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/17f62ed67718954dc8f4c68f7114e5cc.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/17f62ed67718954dc8f4c68f7114e5cc.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/17f62ed67718954dc8f4c68f7114e5cc.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Alith</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An elite huntress from the Underground. She might appear to be sweet and naive, but she is hiding some secrets…  <br>Her mastercraft crossbow allows her to sniper enemies from afar, and her wolf and traps can effectively weaken her prey. </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/343fa2b5e42c605e422ac62fd6fa6b5a.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/343fa2b5e42c605e422ac62fd6fa6b5a.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/343fa2b5e42c605e422ac62fd6fa6b5a.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Jezerin</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The seductive Demon mage. Despite her diabolical appearance, she has a very gentle soul, and the only thing she has to match her look is her exceptional horniness.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the battlefield she weaves destructive fire magics, burning all enemies to crisp in a blink of an eye.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/abe868ddb3e59805fde582db12190a53.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/abe868ddb3e59805fde582db12190a53.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/abe868ddb3e59805fde582db12190a53.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bo</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also known as Black Orchid the Flying Thief, Bo is a femme fatale haunted by bad blood, and she has absolutely no time for bullshits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her proficiency with throwing weapons allows her to perform a wide variety of attacks, not to mention she is very familiar with using poison.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b36fae229f13e639d48bb6a87b285d54.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b36fae229f13e639d48bb6a87b285d54.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/b36fae229f13e639d48bb6a87b285d54.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shanni</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Goblin Shaman who lives alone in the swamp. Despite having the wisdom of a thousand ancestors by her side, she is an absolute nightmare to hangout with due to her toxicity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Her sorcery allows her to put curses on a large area, sucking the life out of everything that dares to linger.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/5876a27dd7ad5cd04d8e17849b229516.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/5876a27dd7ad5cd04d8e17849b229516.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/5876a27dd7ad5cd04d8e17849b229516.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kiritsuki</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An honorable Lizard swordsman from a far away Empire, she is on a suicide mission to hunt down a murderous fiend who slaughtered all her kins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do not be fooled by her elegance, her swordsmanship is a truly deadly art, able to dish out terrible damage in a flash.</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humans are weak! You can’t go anywhere without your STRANGER MAIDENS!<br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/1bda705694778de6ebc64d1975dfc0ce.avif?t=1776310131\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras_big/1bda705694778de6ebc64d1975dfc0ce.webp?t=1776310131 width=1560 height=918 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Game System】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not like your typical Roguelike Survivor, this game focuses on an innovative Squad Based Combat System. Adept to various challenges with a diverse cast of Stranger Maidens, build your ultimate team to eliminate your foes.<br><br>   Explore 19 handcrafted stages, conquer perilous hazards and stage gimmicks, defeat challenging bosses all the while racing against the clock. Utilize the unique &quot;TEAM ROTATION&quot; mechanic to unleash the full potential of the ladies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you want optimize your way to victory, or you just want to hangout with your favorite girls, “Stranger Maidens” will provide you with a satisfying experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/fa14569ae9724fac1eddbd43a397406f.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Story】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as Joey, a loser who was traumatised by the loss of his father. One day you received a mysterious artefact left by your father, and you are determined to go on an adventure to find out what happened to him. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In your journey you will encounter a variety of beautiful yet mysterious Strangers Maidens, each with their own story to tell. Combining their combat prowess and the strange power of the artefact, you come closer to the truth with every step…</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Feature】</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    Tactical Squad Based Combat System provides many possibilities in every battle.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Powerful upgrades await your discovery.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traditional RPG narration style, you get stories both in and out of combat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >19 uniquely designed story stages, 7 fearsome story bosses with unique design and challenge, no more repetitive gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Stranger Maidens each with their own story and unique charm.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 fully hand drawn sex scenes, 12 live2D animated with dynamic cameras.  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/e942100478a70565c639d4d2c6a32f69.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/9d4388097b35111ecd3309510894c94c.mp4?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Stranger Maidens】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/03ee57c239d2cda15988198c2651fb3a.poster.avif?t=1776310131\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/03ee57c239d2cda15988198c2651fb3a.webm?t=1776310131\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028830/extras/03ee57c23